<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>FAQs</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
    integrity="sha384-KK94CHFLLe+nY2dmCWGMq91rCGa5gtU4mk92HdvYe+M/SXH301p5ILy+dN9+nJOZ" crossorigin="anonymous" />
  <!-- Custom CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Style.css" />
</head>
<body class="bg-light text-dark">
  <%- include("partials/header") %>

<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="text-center mb-5">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-5">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted">Answers to common queries about tracking, goals, and your data.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
    <!-- Question 1 -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
          How do I log my meals?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          Go to the <strong>Log Meal</strong> page from the navigation bar. There, you can select from the available menu items for your mess and specify the quantity to log your intake.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Question 2 -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
          How is my BMI calculated?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          BMI is calculated based on the height and weight you provide in your profile. The formula is weight (kg) / [height (m)]Â².
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Question 3 -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
          Can I change my fitness goal?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          Yes, you can change your goal at any time. Go to the <strong>Dashboard</strong> and click on the "Change Goal" button to select a new goal, such as weight loss, maintenance, or muscle gain.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Question 4 -->
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
          How is my leaderboard score calculated?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          Your score is a measure of your consistency over the last 30 days. You earn points for each day you meet your personalized targets for calories, protein, carbs, and fat. The more consistent you are, the higher your score will be!
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>

  <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>